    "The use of the outbuilding hereby permitted as living accommodation shall be for a limited period only from date of approval for a period of 22 months or the completion of the building works to the main dwelling, whichever is the sooner, on or before which date the residential use shall be discontinued, cooking facilities removed and the outbuilding returned to use solely for purposes incidental to the enjoyment of the dwelling house and not for any trade or business nor as living accommodation.",
